# GitHub Flavored Markdown

```elixir
Mix.install([
  {:mdex, "~> 0.8"},
  {:mdex_gfm, "~> 0.1"},
  {:kino, "~> 0.16"},
  {:req, "~> 0.5"}
])
```

## Setup

````elixir
markdown = """
# GitHub Flavored Markdown :eyes:

| Feature | Status |
| ------- | ------ |
| Fast | :white_check_mark: |
| GFM  | :white_check_mark: |

- [x] Task A
- [x] Task B
- [ ] Task C

```elixir
def deps do
  [
    {:mdex, "~> 0.8"}
  ]
end
```

Check out the spec at https://github.github.com/gfm
"""
````

